3^{999999999}\mod 7
p
a \nmid p
a^{p-1} \equiv 1 \mod p.
7 \ \text{is prime and } 3 \nmid 7.
3^6 \equiv 1 \mod 7.
3^{999999999} \equiv 3^{999999996} \cdot 3^3 \equiv \left( 3^6 \right)^{166666666} \cdot 3^3 \equiv 1^{166666666} \cdot 3^3 \equiv 1 \cdot 27 \equiv 6 \mod 7.
3^6\equiv 1 \pmod 7.
999999999 = 166666666 \times 6 + 3
 3^{999999999} \equiv 3^3\equiv 6.
\, {\rm mod}\ 7\!:\ \color{#c00}{3^3\equiv -1}\,\Rightarrow\, (\color{#c00}{3^3})^{333333333}\equiv (\color{#c00}{-1})^{333333333}\equiv -1
